headline: Nike price target lowered to $73 from $78 at TD Cowen
summary: TD Cowen lowered the firm’s price target on Nike (NKE) to $73 from $78 and keeps a Hold rating on the shares. The firm says meetings with channel contacts and field work leave it more cautious on the state of Nike’s business.
